<lb n="0942a11" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0942a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0942a13" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 569</head>
<lb n="0942a14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說心明經<note n="0942002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942002"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0942a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0942a16" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0942003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月氏國三藏＝三藏法師【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏國三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942003"><lem>月氏國三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0942a17" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0942a1701">聞如<app><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【大】">足</rdg></app>。一時佛遊王舍城靈鷲山。與五百比
<lb n="0942a18" ed="T"/>丘四部眾俱。佛以晨旦著衣持&CB00425;。往至一縣
<lb n="0942a19" ed="T"/>而行分衛。諸天龍神追於上侍。到梵志館門
<lb n="0942a20" ed="T"/>外而<note n="0942004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＋（分衛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＋（分衛）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942004"><lem>住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">住分衛</rdg></app>。佛放大光普炤十方。時梵志婦執
<lb n="0942a21" ed="T"/>爨炊飯。見光照身身得安隱。解<note n="0942005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悍＝懌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悍＝懌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942005"><lem>悍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">懌</rdg></app>無量心
<lb n="0942a22" ed="T"/>自念言。今<note n="0942006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝比【元】</note><app n="0942006"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">比</rdg></app>光耀不似日月釋梵四王諸天
<lb n="0942a23" ed="T"/>之明。躬荷熙怡不能自勝。還顧見佛端正<note n="0942007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殊＝姝【元】【明】</note><app n="0942007"><lem>殊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">姝</rdg></app>
<lb n="0942a24" ed="T"/>好。如星中月奇相巍巍。眾好具足諸根澹泊。
<lb n="0942a25" ed="T"/>無有衰入<note n="0942008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">建＝逮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">建＝逮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942008"><lem>建</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">逮</rdg></app>最上寂。得第一定<note n="0942009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如＝始【宮】</note><app n="0942009"><lem>如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">始</rdg></app>日初出
<lb n="0942a26" ed="T"/>現<note n="0942010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">于＝乎【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0942010"><lem>于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">乎</rdg></app>山崗。如轉輪王臨幸大殿<note n="0942011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">補＝寶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">補＝寶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942011"><lem>補</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寶</rdg></app>臣翼從。
<lb n="0942a27" ed="T"/>又若帝釋顯據忉利。猶梵天王於第七尊。如
<lb n="0942a28" ed="T"/>高山雪<note n="0942012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">冏＋（居永反）夾註【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0942012"><lem>冏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">冏<note place="inline">居永反</note></rdg></app>灼普現。倍加踊躍重自<note n="0942013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惟忖＝忖惟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟忖＝忖惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942013"><lem>惟忖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忖惟</rdg></app>。今
<lb n="0942a29" ed="T"/>得&CB00418;佛及<note n="0942014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＝眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942014"><lem>佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眾</rdg></app>弟子誠副宿願。欲以食饌奉進
<pb n="0942b" id="T14.0569.0942b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0942b01" ed="T"/>正覺。隱察愚夫不信道德。志<note n="0942015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">在＝存【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942015"><lem>在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">存</rdg></app>邪疑六十
<lb n="0942b02" ed="T"/>二見。見<note n="0942016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妾＝我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妾＝我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942016"><lem>妾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我</rdg></app>所施必興結恨。宿命愆咎失雄
<lb n="0942b03" ed="T"/>猛男。嬰墜女像羈制於人。欲施聖尊不得由
<lb n="0942b04" ed="T"/>已。宜順護意當如之何。便即<note n="0942017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">箄＝捍【宋】，壓【元】【明】，捭【宮】</note><note n="0942017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">箄＝捍【宋】，＝壓【元】【明】，＝捭【宮】</note><app n="0942017"><lem>箄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">捍</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">壓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">捭</rdg></app>飯取汁一杓
<lb n="0942b05" ed="T"/>以用上佛。佛之威神。&CB00425;中自然有百味食。佛
<lb n="0942b06" ed="T"/>時達嚫。口歎頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0942b07" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0942b0701"><l>假以馬百疋</l><l>金銀挍鞍勒</l>
<lb n="0942b08" ed="T"/><l>用惠施於人</l><l>不如杓飯汁</l>
<lb n="0942b09" ed="T"/><l>設以七寶車</l><l>載滿諸<note n="0942018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">珍琦＝琦珍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珍琦＝琦珍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942018"><lem>珍琦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">琦珍</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0942b10" ed="T"/><l>杓飯汁施佛</l><l>其福過於彼</l>
<lb n="0942b11" ed="T"/><l>若施白象百</l><l>明珠瓔珞飾</l>
<lb n="0942b12" ed="T"/><l>供佛一杓汁</l><l>其福超彼上</l>
<lb n="0942b13" ed="T"/><l>如聖轉輪王</l><l>普賢玉女后</l>
<lb n="0942b14" ed="T"/><l>端正無有比</l><l>七寶瓔珞身</l>
<lb n="0942b15" ed="T"/><l>如是之妙類</l><l>其數各有百</l>
<lb n="0942b16" ed="T"/><l>悉以配施人</l><l>不如一杓汁</l></lg>
<lb n="0942b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0942b1701">於時梵志靜住而聽聞佛所歎。心懷疑惑前
<lb n="0942b18" ed="T"/>問佛言。一杓飯汁何所直也而乃稱讚。若干
<lb n="0942b19" ed="T"/>寶施象馬車乘。不可<note n="0942019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呰毀＝訾數【元】，言數【明】</note><note n="0942019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呰毀＝訾數【元】，＝言數【明】</note><app n="0942019"><lem>呰毀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">訾數</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">言數</rdg></app>而云不如杓飯汁
<lb n="0942b20" ed="T"/>施。斯之飯汁不直一錢。然乃咨嗟若干億倍
<lb n="0942b21" ed="T"/>孰當信哉。</p>
<lb n="0942b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0942b2201">於是世尊。尋即顯露廣長之舌。以覆其面上
<lb n="0942b23" ed="T"/>至梵天。告梵志曰。吾從無數億百千劫。常
<lb n="0942b24" ed="T"/>行至誠六度無極。施諸所安有而不惜乃獲
<lb n="0942b25" ed="T"/>斯舌。寧以妄語能致之乎。吾欲問卿至誠答
<lb n="0942b26" ed="T"/>之。曾頗往返舍衛羅閱。中路<note n="0942020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（見）＋有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（見）＋有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942020"><lem>有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見有</rdg></app>樹名尼拘
<lb n="0942b27" ed="T"/>類。蔭庇人眾五百乘車<note n="0942021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乎＝不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎＝不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942021"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不</rdg></app>。對曰唯然。有是
<lb n="0942b28" ed="T"/><note n="0942022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔樹我〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔樹我〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942022"><lem>樹我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>所見也。世尊又問其子大如。答曰形
<lb n="0942b29" ed="T"/>如芥子。佛告梵志。卿真兩舌。實如芥子樹何
<pb n="0942c" id="T14.0569.0942c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0942c01" ed="T"/><note n="0942023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">巨乎＝巨大【宋】【宮】，大乎【元】【明】</note><note n="0942023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巨乎＝巨大【宋】【宮】，＝大乎【元】【明】</note><app n="0942023"><lem>巨乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">巨大</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">大乎</rdg></app>。對曰審爾不敢欺也。佛又告曰。種如
<lb n="0942c02" ed="T"/>芥子生樹廣大。地之生<note n="0942024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殖＝植【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殖＝植【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942024"><lem>殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">植</rdg></app>適無所置所覆彌
<lb n="0942c03" ed="T"/>廣。乃<note n="0942025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">況＝爾況復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">況＝爾況復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942025"><lem>況</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">爾況復</rdg></app>如來無上至真等正覺。無量福會普
<lb n="0942c04" ed="T"/>勝者哉。戒定慧<note n="0942026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">解脫＝脫脫【宋】【元】，解度【宮】</note><note n="0942026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">解脫＝脫脫【宋】【元】，＝解度【宮】</note><app n="0942026"><lem>解脫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">脫脫</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">解度</rdg></app><note n="0942027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔解脫〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔解脫〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942027"><lem>解脫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>知見事。大慈弘
<lb n="0942c05" ed="T"/>哀無所不濟。以饌供獻<note n="0942028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">功＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">功＝福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942028"><lem>功</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">福</rdg></app>祚難計。梵志默然
<lb n="0942c06" ed="T"/>無以加報。時佛乃笑。五色光從口出。照十方
<lb n="0942c07" ed="T"/>五趣之類。<note n="0942029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝夫【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0942029"><lem>天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">夫</rdg></app>欲<note n="0942030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">止＝至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止＝至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942030"><lem>止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至</rdg></app>人心喜。餓鬼<note n="0942031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飽＋（滿）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飽＋（滿）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942031"><lem>飽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飽滿</rdg></app>地獄
<lb n="0942c08" ed="T"/>痛息。畜生意開罪除。尋光來詣佛所。諸佛
<lb n="0942c09" ed="T"/>笑法皆有常瑞。授菩薩決。遍照十方光從頂
<lb n="0942c10" ed="T"/>入。授緣覺&CB00028;光入面門。授聲聞&CB00028;光入肩斗。
<lb n="0942c11" ed="T"/>說生天事光從&CB00685;入。說降人中光從膝入。說
<lb n="0942c12" ed="T"/>趣三苦<note n="0942032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（光）＋從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（光）＋從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942032"><lem>從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">光從</rdg></app>足心入。諸佛之欣。不以欲笑。不
<lb n="0942c13" ed="T"/>以瞋笑。不以癡笑。不放逸笑。不利欲笑。不
<lb n="0942c14" ed="T"/>榮貴笑。不富饒笑。今佛普等愍傷群萌。行
<lb n="0942c15" ed="T"/>大慈笑無斯七也。賢者阿難分別七法。知法
<lb n="0942c16" ed="T"/>解義曉時了節暢眾會事。<note n="0942033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＝思【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自＝思【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942033"><lem>自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">思</rdg></app>省己身明眾人
<lb n="0942c17" ed="T"/>根。即從座起更整衣服長跪問佛。佛何<note n="0942034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">因＋（緣）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">因＋（緣）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942034"><lem>因</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">因緣</rdg></app>
<lb n="0942c18" ed="T"/>笑願說其意。佛告阿難。見梵志婦發大意乎。
<lb n="0942c19" ed="T"/>對曰已見。佛言。斯婦壽終。當轉女像<note n="0942035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得＝後【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942035"><lem>得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後</rdg></app>為
<lb n="0942c20" ed="T"/>男子。生于天上諸天中尊。下生世間為人中
<lb n="0942c21" ed="T"/>上。解深妙法如幻如化如水中月影響野馬。
<lb n="0942c22" ed="T"/>&CB00230;三十劫當得作佛。名曰心明如來至真等
<lb n="0942c23" ed="T"/>正覺明行成為善逝世間解無上士道法御天
<lb n="0942c24" ed="T"/>人師號佛世尊。梵志心伏五體投地剋心自
<lb n="0942c25" ed="T"/>責。懺曰。我如小兒愚癡闇冥。懷疑猶豫不識
<lb n="0942c26" ed="T"/>大聖。口出&CB00308;言唯原罪釁佛言。善哉善哉。若
<lb n="0942c27" ed="T"/>自見過歸命於佛。於道法律悔殃塵者。其咎
<lb n="0942c28" ed="T"/>損<note n="0942036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">減＝滅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">減＝滅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942036"><lem>減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">滅</rdg></app>福增日滋。梵志<note n="0942037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">進啟＝啟進【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">進啟＝啟進【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942037"><lem>進啟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">啟進</rdg></app>。唯垂大哀加恩
<lb n="0942c29" ed="T"/>矜攝令得出家。佛即納受以為沙門。鬚髮則
<pb n="0943a" id="T14.0569.0943a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0943a01" ed="T"/>除法衣在身。於時世尊。講四聖諦苦<note n="0943001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">習＝集【元】【明】</note><app n="0943001"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡
<lb n="0943a02" ed="T"/>道。梵志踊躍漏盡意解。佛說如是。賢者阿難。
<lb n="0943a03" ed="T"/>諸四部眾。天人龍神。皆發道意。歡喜<note n="0943002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">稽首＋（而退）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0943002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稽首＋（而退）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0943002"><lem>稽首</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">稽首而退</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0943a04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說心明經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>